sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant G as Guest Browser (bluee.localhost)
  participant FE as Frontend /jobs
  participant BFF as back-bluee
  participant ORG as organizations (RMQ)
  participant TAL as talent (RMQ)
  participant DB as MongoDB

  G->>FE: GET /jobs
  FE->>FE: obtener slug desde host (bluee)
  FE->>BFF: GET /organizations/public/by-slug/bluee
  BFF->>ORG: RMQ organizations.get-by-slug
  ORG->>DB: findOne({ identity.slug: "bluee" })
  ORG-->>BFF: organización (_id tenantId)
  BFF-->>FE: tenantId resuelto

  FE->>BFF: GET /requisitions/public?tenantId=<org._id>
  BFF->>TAL: RMQ requisitions.list
  TAL->>DB: listar por tenantId
  TAL-->>BFF: requisiciones
  BFF->>BFF: filtrar publicadas (recruiting + site_web)
  BFF-->>FE: vacantes públicas
  FE-->>G: render listado de jobs

